<sect1 id="Annotator.ValueGraph">
	<title>Display Series Data on Concepts</title>
	<para>
		Replaces node icons with bar charts or line graphs of series data
		assigned to
		concepts, for example Log ratios from micro-array
		expression.
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center"
						fileref="../images/annotator/annotator_valueGraph1.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>
		A user can select how to group data into each series.
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center"
						fileref="../images/annotator/annotator_valueGraph2.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>
		It is possible to change the colour for each series by clicking
		in the corresponding field.
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center"
						fileref="../images/annotator/annotator_valueGraph3.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>
		After clicking on Annotate Graph
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center"
						fileref="../images/annotator/annotator_valueGraph4.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
</sect1>